<i>noun</i>: 광산 [광ː산] <i>verb</i>: 채굴하다 [채ː굴하다] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>광산 [광ː산]</dt><br>
<dd>mine</dd><br>
<dd>광물을 캐내는 곳.</dd><br>
<dd>A place to dig for minerals.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>채굴하다 [채ː굴하다]</dt><br>
<dd>mine</dd><br>
<dd>땅속에 묻혀 있는 광물 등을 캐내다.</dd><br>
<dd>To extract metals, minerals, etc., from the ground.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>